    <outline text="Physical weakness of database/server room/location. #A1 "/>
    <outline text="Irresponsible behaviour/negligeable"/>
</outline>
<outline text="What are threats, relevant to the assets (and vulnerabilities)?">
    <outline text="How can students attack the scheme?">
        <outline text="gain physical access to the data and forge someone's public key. #A1"/>
        <outline text="have phone being stolen or lost, leading to leakage of private key. #A2"/>
        <outline text="malicious student can sell their keys to the dark web. #A3"/>
